posting_body: ['CALL US TODAY!', 'show contact info', 'x251', 'SYCAMORE COMMONS APARTMENTS', '2 bedroom 1 bath \xa0 965Sq.', 'Ft \xa0 $2,600', 'DESCRIPTION:', 'Experience elevated apartment living in the Bay Area when you move into this two-bedroom, one-bathroom apartment at Sycamore Commons!', 'Both bedrooms feature an oversized walk-in closet for all of your storage needs.', 'In the shared bathroom, you’ll find a dual vanity set and a refreshing tub.', 'Across from the dining area, the stylish galley kitchen comes with a tiled backsplash, a breakfast bar, and stainless steel appliances.', 'The living room is just as impressive with modern ceiling fixtures, energy-efficient lights, and hardwood flooring.', 'As an added perk, a private deck or patio gives you even more space to relax.', 'At Sycamore Commons, on-site conveniences include three laundry facilities, a heated pool, and the support of a reliable management and maintenance team.', 'The community is also just minutes away from Tom Maloney Elementary and Centerville Junior High School.', 'Speak to a leasing agent for more details!', 'Sycamore Commons A Place to Call Home!', 'Address:', '38655 Paseo Padre Pkwy Fremont, CA 94536', 'Website:', '<URL>/']
